data.description: Beautiful home in the highly sought after Tower Grove South neighborhood. 2 bedrooms / 2.5 bathrooms. Notice the gorgeous details throughout… crown molding, period millwork, ornamental clapboards, 9’ ceilings, hardwood flooring, recessed lighting… The living room features a cozy sitting nook & decorative fireplace. Separate dining room off the kitchen. Kitchen has stainless steel appliances & a large pantry/bar area. Half bath on the main floor. Master bedroom has a vaulted ceiling, 2 closets, built-in cabinet, & the French doors open up the balcony. Heated floor in upstairs full bathroom. Finished, walk-up, lower level with full bathroom, rec/living room, & a wet bar. Private, fenced yard with a large 2-car garage. 2 short blocks from Tower Grove Park & surrounded by restaurants. Owner is now engaged & they will be buying a home together in a different area for job locations. He will miss living here but was good while it lasted. This is truly a gem! And a great lifestyle!
